303 DAYS UNTIL A4!!

2 DAYS UNTIL AMATW!

i just finished amatw bc it comes out two days earlier in the philippines and i ONE HUNDRED PERCENT RECOMMEND IT. IT WAS SO GREAT. IT WAS SO HILARIOUS. IT WAS SO CUTE. GOD I LOVE THEM ALL WITH ALL MY HEART AND SOUL

ok so i’m gonna copy and paste from my twitter WARNING: SPOILERS!!!

I’M FUCKING SOBBING I JUST WATCHED ANT-MAN AND THE WASP⁠ IT’S SO GOOD I CRIED THE FIRST 5 MINUTES SCOTTY AND CASSIE THEY’RE SO CUTE I WAS ACTUALLY CRYING

do i need to even mention the mid credit scene

summary: Thor The Exterminator
title: Thor The Exterminator
body:
Based on this headcanon 

@imagine-mcu wanted to be tagged in stories so here ya go~

You sitting on your bed, wearing a tank top and sweatpants reading a book before you turned into bed. You were just getting to the climax when a black blurb slowly moving down in your vision. You thought your vision was playing tricks on you, but you were proven wrong when the spider tried to swing it’s way onto your book. You noticed the tiny critter and threw your book across the room and sprang out of your bed screaming.

Thor came bursting through your door– no literally, he just slammed his body through the door, shattering it to pieces. He was the first to come to your room, naturally as his room was across from yours. “What is it, Lady, [Y/N]!” The god boomed. “I heard you screaming.”

You pouted your mouth, pointing to the bug while whimpering. “There’s a spider. Please kill it.”

He paused for a moment, processing what you had said, before smiling. “Of course, [Y/N]!” He Laughed, pointing Mjölnir above your bed, summoning lighting.

“No wait, Thor, don’t!” You tried to stop him, but it was too late. A burst of lighting came from the hammer, setting your room ablaze. You stood in horror, along with the other avengers staring wanting to know why your room was on fire.

“I’ll get the fire extinguisher.” Clit sighed, walking off to do as he said.

“Do you think I killed it?” Thor asked innocent as could be.

Your eyes welled with tears and you almost broke down when you felt a gentle hand on your shoulder.  “Why don’t we get you set up in one of the spare rooms, hm?” You nodded slowly and walked away from your room as it went up in ashes.

You were now sitting in the room reserved for new members or visitors. As such, it had plain word floors and light grey walls with very basic furniture. You would be spending a while here until your room was fixed. Best part? You couldn’t even decorate in the meantime.

Tony was able to fast order you a new copy of the book your were reading and you tried to find your spot. Just before you found it, you saw a black blur in your vision. Whether or not it was the same spider from your room, you didn’t know or care. You took a deep breath and let out a heavy sigh. You slammed the book closed on the spider before shutting the lights off and going to sleep after a very long and eventful night.






I hope you enjoyed! Didn’t enjoy it? Please tell me what you didn’t like about it so I can improve myself as a writer for next time<3

I take requests!

Tony was able to fast order you a new copy of the book your were reading and you tried to find your spot. Just before you found it, you saw a black blur in your vision. Whether or not it was the same spider from your room, you didn’t know or care. You took a deep breath and let out a heavy sigh. You slammed the book closed on the spider before shutting the lights off and going to sleep after a very long and eventful night.
